item.title: CVE-2023-0178|2024-08-02T05:02:43.799Z -- unknown -- annual%20archive
item.description: The Annual Archive WordPress plugin before 1.6.0 does not validate and escape some of its shortcode attributes before outputting them back in a page/post where the shortcode is embed, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks.
